  "fullArabic": "سَأَصۡرِفُ عَنۡ ءَايَٰتِيَ ٱلَّذِينَ يَتَكَبَّرُونَ فِي ٱلۡأَرۡضِ بِغَيۡرِ ٱلۡحَقِّ وَإِن يَرَوۡاْ كُلَّ ءَايَةٖ لَّا يُؤۡمِنُواْ بِهَا وَإِن يَرَوۡاْ سَبِيلَ ٱلرُّشۡدِ لَا يَتَّخِذُوهُ سَبِيلٗا وَإِن يَرَوۡاْ سَبِيلَ ٱلۡغَيِّ يَتَّخِذُوهُ سَبِيلٗاۚ ذَٰلِكَ بِأَنَّهُمۡ كَذَّبُواْ بِ‍َٔايَٰتِنَا وَكَانُواْ عَنۡهَا غَٰفِلِينَ",
  "fullTranslation": "I will turn away from My signs those who are arrogant upon the earth without right; and if they should see every sign, they will not believe in it. And if they see the way of consciousness, they will not adopt it as a way; but if they see the way of error, they will adopt it as a way. That is because they have denied Our signs and they were heedless of them.",
  "fullTransliteration": "sa-asrifu an ayatiya alladhina yatakabbaruna fi al-ardi bighayri al-haqi wa-in yaraw kulla ayatin la yu'minu biha wa-in yaraw sabila al-rush'di la yattakhidhuhu sabilan wa-in yaraw sabila al-ghayi yattakhidhuhu sabilan dhalika bi-annahum kadhabu biayatina wakanu anha ghafilina"
}
